message.content: The stud finder is a crucial tool in construction and home improvement, enabling users to locate wall studs with high accuracy. It comes in magnetic and electronic varieties, with the former detecting metal fasteners and the latter sensing changes in wall density to identify studs, pipes, and wires. While magnetic stud finders are simple and battery-free, they can mistakenly detect other metal objects.
